  "contents": "<div class=\"content markitup-box\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t按理来说，中华民国(台湾)是东亚对抗独裁威权政体(中华人民共和国)的最前线，应该很多国家会给予中华民国(台湾)护照高待遇吧？但是为啥在认可度上，中华民国(台湾)护照却不如香港护照呢？(中华民国护照比起港澳的护照多了一个免签国美国，但港澳护照可以免签前苏联国家和一些拉丁美洲国家)。<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvNzNhYWUxMTgwYTc2MmRmMGNhOGZiLnBuZz93aWR0aD0xNDI1JmhlaWdodD02MjU\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/73aae1180a762df0ca8fb.png?width=1425&amp;height=625\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/73aae1180a762df0ca8fb.png?width=1425&amp;height=625\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/73aae1180a762df0ca8fb.png?width=1425&amp;height=625\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvM2U0ZjY3NGFlZTI4M2VjZDllNWE4LnBuZz93aWR0aD0xNDI1JmhlaWdodD02MjU\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/3e4f674aee283ecd9e5a8.png?width=1425&amp;height=625\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/3e4f674aee283ecd9e5a8.png?width=1425&amp;height=625\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/3e4f674aee283ecd9e5a8.png?width=1425&amp;height=625\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvYzZjYTM4NjI0YzExNzYyZTIzYzgxLnBuZz93aWR0aD0xNDI1JmhlaWdodD02MjU\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/c6ca38624c11762e23c81.png?width=1425&amp;height=625\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/c6ca38624c11762e23c81.png?width=1425&amp;height=625\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/c6ca38624c11762e23c81.png?width=1425&amp;height=625\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvNDk3ZjNlYzg4NjZlOWFkMDQwYzY0LnBuZz93aWR0aD0xNDI1JmhlaWdodD02MjU\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/497f3ec8866e9ad040c64.png?width=1425&amp;height=625\"><img a